high_descs: Turn right and stop in front of the green chair with the lap top on it.
Close the top of the lap top and pick it up.
Turn around and face the bed on the right with the white pillows.
Place the lap top down on the bed next to the right of the white pillow that's closest to you.
Turn right, turn left at the television, walk to the other side of the desk to face the lap top.
Close the top of the lap top and pick it up.
Walk over to the same white pillow as before.
Place the lap top to the left of the white pillow.
anns.task_desc: Put two laptops on the bed.

high_descs: Walk over to the green chair and close the computer
Pick the computer up from the green chair
Carry the computer over to the bed and place it on top of the bed next to the pillow
Walk over to the table on the the other side of the room
close the top on the computer
Pick the computer up from the table
Carry the computer over to the bed that has the other computer on it
Place that computer on the opposite side of the pillow
anns.task_desc: Gather the computers up and place them on the bed

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the green chair on your left.
Close the lap top lid and pick up the lap top from the chair.
Turn around, head towards the other green chair, and then turn right towards the bed.
Place the lap top to the right of the pillow on the bed.
Walk towards the end of the black table on your right and find the lap top on it.
Close the lap top lid and pick it up from the desk.
Turn around and head towards the bed.
Place the lap top on the left side of the pillow.
anns.task_desc: Place the two lap tops on the bed.

high_descs: Turn right, walk across the room, then turn to the left to face an arm chair with a lap top on it.
Close the lap top on the arm chair and then pick it up.
Turn around, walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the bed.
Put the lap top on the right side of the pillow.
Turn to the right, walk across the room, turn to the left, walk across the room, turn to the right, walk across the room, turn to the right and walk forward to face the table.
Pick up the lap top on the table.
Turn to the right, take two steps, turn to the left, walk across the room, turn to the right and take a step, then turn right to face the bed.
Place the lap top on the left side of the pillow.
anns.task_desc: To put two lap tops on the bed.
